TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Waiter, there are no Dank Memes in my MLG soup!

Edited November 15, 2015 by Sanic

You didn't order any.

Waiter, there's a Mortimer Kerman in my soup!

He said he'd give me (as the waiter) 1,000,000,000,000,000 Funds if he could commit soup-o-cide due to all his stress. I guess he's invincible if he's still alive...

Waiter! Why are you in my soup, in the form of a sea serpent?!

Oh, I'm just...Um, I'm just checking your dental health. And also to heat your soup with my dragon breath.

Waiter! There's a miniature death star armed with all kinds of destructive weapons in my soup!

Sir, that is a pea.

Waiter, there is a SpaceplaneHater in my soup!

It seems to be going on a rant about how bad spaceplanes are. Just throw it out.

Waiter, my soup has become a solid block!

Welcome to Minecraft, my friend!

Waiter, there's an unwanted multicellular organism of insectoid descent whose death was recent and most likely caused by it being unable to obtain oxygen from the atmosphere in my pool of essentially hydric acid, natrium chloride, lipids and plant cells contained within a solid container.

So there's a fly in your soup. It's there to add protein.

Waiter, there's a lumpy brown mass in my soup!

Throw it away, its extra weight.

Waiter! I'm in my soup!

You did order the bathtub special, sir.

Waiter! There's a Saturn-V replica in my soup!

That's how you get to Moon-lily soup, sir. 

Waiter! There's a Corvette in my soup!

That's because you ordered the "Antique Special" Sir.

 

Waiter! Dres is in my soup!

What's Dres?

Waiter! There's a clothespin in my soup!

The Pin Soup comes with a free clothespin!'

Waiter, there's a Fargo in my soup!

Who is dat guy?

Waiter there is a copy of  ksp pre-release 1.1! *takes it*

*takes it away* Ah ah ah. It's not released yet.

Waiter! There's a pirate ship in my soup!

19 minutes ago, Maximus97 said:

Waiter! There's a pirate ship in my soup!

Said God, as he looked upon the Carribean Gulf...

 

Waiter! Plato's Cave is in my soup!

Did you say Pluto? Pluto comes in many soups. Plato's cave? That's one soggy book..[

Waiter! There's a Steve Buscemi in my soup!

OH NO! WE THOUGHT IT WAS CHICKEN! *Breaks into a sob*

 

Waiter! My soul is in my soup!

I can tell, your body looks pretty lifeless...

Waiter! There's a waiter in my soup!

I'll be out in a moment, sir, sorry for the inconvenience.

Waiter! There's a non sequitur in my soup!

Live with it! Fish it out and put it in a napkin if you can.

Waiter, there's a staaarrmaaann waiting in my soup!

♫ He'd like to come and meet us, but he thinks he'd blow our minds. ♫

Waiter, there's some intelligence in my soup!

Lech. Where'd that come from?

Waiter, there's a book in my soup. I think it's called...Something-Nomicon.

Aha yes. A very good read! 

Waiter theres a Dres in my soup!
